	   <tr><td colspan=2>Paladins have a good Magic Resist due to the cleric buffs, making SK fear and other things uselss.&nbsp;&nbsp;also, LoH cant be resisted while Harm Touch can be.<br><br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
