	   <tr><td colspan=2>I am currently a Lvl12 Dwarven Paladin.&nbsp;&nbsp;What I am hoping is that some of you will be able to help me out with some equipment questions.<br><br>1.  I currently have both a DwarvenMace and a Broadsword.  Both Skills were maxxed out at L11.  I just made L12, so have not had a chance to max them both at 12.  My questions is if anyone knows where a L12 paladin can solo to get some magical weapons (near to Freeport area would be best as I am currently in North Ro).  If  need to buy them, I only have 50Plat.<br><br>2.  I am also currently wearing only Leather Armor and see many discussions here about other Paladins around my level asking if they should be upgrading to Fine Steel armor.  My question on this topic is where does a low-level paladin get the money to purchase (or where does he find) Fine Steel Plate Armor.  I have looked at the shops in Kaladim and all the prices are around 200-300 Plat per piece.<br><br>3.  I have chosen to pursue Blacksmithing as a Trade skill and would like some advice on when I should start working on that skill.<br><br><br>Trystam<br>L12 Dwarven Paladin<br>Charter Member:  Chaos Engine Guild<br>Innoruuk Server<br>&nbsp;<br> </td></tr>
